        "collapsible_tab_PAyNwP": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "BassFlow Vent Pressure System",
            "content": "<p>A small vent sits in front of the isobaric bass drivers. It releases canal pressure on long sessions and shapes how the bass moves — how quickly it settles, how much body it carries, and how cleanly it hands off to the mids. Bass keeps its weight and texture without the trapped pressure that closed designs can build up over an hour of listening.</p>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_n38dzJ": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Dual Isobaric Dynamic Woofer",
            "content": "<p>Two 6mm dynamic drivers sit in an isobaric arrangement — twin diaphragms moving in step, sharing the load. The pair distorts less than a single driver of the same size and reaches lower with cleaner texture. A passive filter limits the woofer to the bottom octaves so the balanced armatures stay clear to handle mids and treble. The intent is bass you feel without bass that smudges the rest of the music.</p>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_HffCBq": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "3D Printed Enclosure and Precision Engineering",
            "content": "<p>The Z06 shell is AAW's third digital enclosure platform. Driver positions, chamber volumes, and nozzle geometry are iterated in simulation before any acrylic is printed — the same shell shape, the same internal acoustics, build after build. Every pair is printed, hand-finished, and measured in our Singapore workshop before it ships.</p>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_XefaKL": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Accessories and Warranty",
            "content": "<p>48\" Null Audio Epsilon UPOCC Copper Detachable Cable<br/>AAW Carrying Case<br/>3 Pairs SpinFit Silicone Tip(S/M/L)*<br/>3 Pairs AAW Short Stem Foam Tips(S/M/L)*<br/>6 Pairs AAW Assorted Silicone Tips (S/M/LX2)*<br/>1 Year Limited Warranty</p><p></p><p>* For Universal Fit Only</p>"
          }
        },
        "specification_gbeGJd": {
